      "name": "Hemolysis index validation against FDA benchmark experimental data",
      "description": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against published FDA benchmark experimental measurements for the generic centrifugal blood pump across 5 operating points. RH < 1 criterion satisfied for all evaluated conditions."
